title: Wish Kid - The Complete Series
description:
When a shooting star from outer space blazes into Nick's room one day, hitting his baseball glove and rendering it magic, he is granted one wish a week, launching him from one adventure to another! Join Nick and his best friend, Darryl, on exciting and sometimes troublesome escapades as they chase ghosts, become Top Gun pilots, escape from aliens, become superheroes and so much more all while trying to stay away from the neighborhood bully.

Episode List:

Top Gun - Will Travel
A Matter of Principal
Haunted House for Sale
Captain Mayhem
Glove of Dreams
Love At First Wish
Lotto Trouble
Darryl's Dilemma
A Nick Off The Old Block
A Grand Ol' Time
Gross Encounters
Mom, Dad, You're Fired!
The Best of Enemies
